Class NativeNodeContainer

    public class NativeNodeContainer
extends SingleNodeContainer
    Implementation of SingleNodeContainer for a natively implemented KNIME Node relying on a NodeModel.

    2.9
    Author:
    B. Wiswedel & M.Berthold
